{
  "img": "icons/weapons/staves/staff-skull-feathers-brown.webp",
  "name": "Staff of Hungry Shadows",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>This staff is made of scorched and twisted wood and is set with a crystal sphere filled with swirling smoke. While wielding the staff, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to checks to identify necromancy magic.</p><p>The staff also functions as a +2 greater striking staff.</p><hr /><p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">D</span> (concentrate, interact)</p><p><strong>Effect</strong> You cast @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Summon Undead]{Summon Undead} to summon a dread wraith.</p><hr /><p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p><p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</p><ul><li><strong>Cantrip</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Void Warp]{Void Warp}</li><li><strong>1st</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Enfeeble]{Enfeeble}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Grim Tendrils]{Grim Tendrils}</li><li><strong>2nd</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Darkness]{Darkness}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Ghostly Carrier]{Ghostly Carrier}</li><li><strong>3rd</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Blindness]{Blindness}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Vampiric Feast]{Vampiric Feast}</li><li><strong>4th</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Vapor Form]{Vapor Form}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Shape Stone]{Shape Stone}</li><li><strong>5th</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Shadow Siphon]{Shadow Siphon}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Black Tentacles]{Black Tentacles}</li></ul>"
    },
